data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Crete, IL! This stunning 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom residence, built just two years ago, offers a modern design. The open floor plan, gas fireplace in living room, eat in kitchen, and spacious bedrooms provide ample living space for the whole family. Enjoy the fenced backyard perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining. Located in a charming community with easy access to amenities, this home is a must-see. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this your own!
